	* e-shortcuts-view.c (e_shortcuts_view_construct): Ooops.  We were
	reffing a bogus pointer that was not assigned yet.

	* e-corba-storage-registry.c (impl_StorageRegistry_addStorage):
	Updated according to the new IDL.

