	`EStoragePrivate'.
	(init): Init to NULL.
	(destroy): Unref.
	(e_storage_construct): New arg @toplevel_node_type.  Set the
	private member value accordingly.
	(e_storage_new): New arg @toplevel_node_type.  Pass to
	`e_storage_construct'.
	(e_storage_get_toplevel_node_type): New.

